    "ron_burgundy_voice": "Well, well, well. Look at these two gentlemen, engaged in what appears to be a rather\u2026 prolonged exchange of the pickleball. It's like watching paint dry, but with more athletic shorts. Truly, a spectacle for the ages. Stay classy, pickleball court.",
